      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀加速，交易员认为英国央行降息幅度较小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示通胀10个月来首次意外上升后，交易员大幅削减了对英国央行降息的押注，英国债券大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达沃斯直播：摩根大通仍在为华尔街招聘救济人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管华尔街一直在谈论裁员，但摩根大通表示已计划增加员工人数，而瑞银集团董事长则对影子银行发出警告，试图在世界经济论坛上转移监管机构的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
